    Create Pick Your Poison Executable As SophosMDR  ${permissions}

Create Pick Your Poison Argument File
    [Arguments]  ${arg}
    Create File   ${PickYourPoisonArgFile}    content=${arg}

Create Pick Your Poison Executable As SophosMDR
